<paragraph blockId="41.[205,1414,707,1647]" pageId="41" pageNumber="593">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[207,926,1381,1410]" pageId="41" pageNumber="593">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but the Peruvian Toro is arboreal.
