</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="41" pageNumber="593" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="41.[205,1414,707,1647]" pageId="41" pageNumber="593">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[207,554,1456,1489]" pageId="41" pageNumber="593">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Additional studies on distribution, habitat, ecology, abundance, and conservation threats to the Peruvian Toro are needed.
</paragraph>
